  "reviews": "\u201cMountain breaks the mold of video games.\u201d<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2014/07/you-are-mountain/374543/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >The Atlantic</a></a><br><br>\u201cNothing You Do Matters in This Game, But You\u2019ll Still Obsess Over It.\u201d<br><a href=\"http://www.wired.com/2014/07/mountain-game\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >WIRED</a></a><br><br>\u201cAt the beginning of the game, I find the idea cute. By the end, I am hypnotized.\u201d<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/arts/miranda/la-et-cam-playing-her-animator-david-oreilly-mountain-video-game-20140705-column.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >LA Times</a></a><br>",
